## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full scope of ongoing scientific research. Additionally, while there is a strong consensus on human-caused climate change, some dissenting opinions exist, though they are in the minority. The report also does not delve into the potential solutions or mitigation strategies, focusing solely on the causative factors.

